OL,3,CMan charged with multiple counts of
OL,4,Crape and sex offences against two women
OL,6,FA man has been charged with multiple
OL,7,Fcounts of rape and a string of other
OL,8,Fsex offences against two women.
OL,10,FAndrew Dent, 54, has been charged with
OL,11,Fnine counts of rape, five counts of
OL,12,Fsexual assault by penetration, three
OL,13,Fcounts of intentional strangulation,
OL,14,Ftwo counts of assault occasioning
OL,15,Factual bodily harm and one count of
OL,16,Fvoyeurism.
