OL,3,CMan charged with multiple counts of
OL,4,Crape and sex offences against two women
OL,6,FThe charges relate to two women in
OL,7,FBerkshire, who allege they were
OL,8,Fattacked on separate occasions after
OL,9,Fmeeting a man on a dating website or
OL,10,Fapp.
OL,12,FOne of the women, in her 30s, was
OL,13,Fallegedly attacked and had intimate
OL,14,Fphotographs of her taken without her
OL,15,Fconsent in a hotel in West Berkshire
OL,16,Fon the evening of 19 June 2024, police
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
